[matlab_inverse]
    Inverse routing method source code

[input/<basin>.inputs]
    Inputs for inverse routing for a certain basin

[output/<basin>]
    Direct outputs from inverse routing

[scripts]
    All scripts for pre-process, post-process, result analysis, etc.
    See 'README_file_structure' for detailed script usage

[data]
    Original or processed streamflow data

[postprocess_results] -> Need to change data structure!!
    Results for result checking/analysis
    Including:
        - Lohman routing parameters and results;
        - Processed inverse-routed total runoff;
        - Plots;
        - etc.  

